      "text": [
        " : \"لاَ يَجُوزُ اَلْعَرَبُونُ إِلاَّ أَنْ يَكُونَ نَقْداً مِنَ اَلثَّمَنِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3750 - Wahb ibn Wahb narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) (peace be upon them), that Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) used to say:\n\"Earnest money (down payment) is not permissible unless it is part of the price.\""
        ]
      }
